en_492865_0	A large gathering of troops in Kilinochchi and students at Aravinagar faculty of the Jaffna University participated in a “Music Therapy” programme on Saturday (2) at Nelumpiyasa auditorium, organized by the SFHQ -KLN on the instructions of the Commander Security Forces Kilinochchi, Major General G.V. Ravipriya.
en_492865_1	The veteran musician, Mr. K Pradeep Bogahawatte and members of the Crescendo Music Institution carried out the project.
en_492865_2	Commander Security Forces Kilinochchi graced the event as the Chief Guest along with Senior Officers and Officers.
en_492865_3	More than 1500 participated in the music therapy programme.
